reviewText: I would still like to get this program as I think it would be useful; however, after trying twice and getting what looked like the right DVD (it was labeled right but the actual program on the disc was wrong) I've pretty much surrendered that it's not going to happen. Both discs were labeled as the Beauty of Ugly but actually contained the Adaptive Animal Anatomy program (which I already have) - if I thought I might actually get the right program I'd try again - the other program (adaptive animal anatomy) is pretty good but I only need one copy of it
